@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="flip-card-container">
    <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
                <h3>Data Protection</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
                <p>We ensure your data is securely stored and handled according to industry standards.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
                <h3>Encrypted Storage</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
                <p>All sensitive information is encrypted to prevent unauthorized access.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
                <h3>Transparency</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
                <p>We are open about how your data is collected, used, and protected.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
                <h3>Your Rights</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
                <p>You have full control over your data, including access, correction, and deletion rights.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h2> Information We Collect  </h2>
<p>We collect information neccessary to provide our room hire services. including.</p>
<p> 1. Contact details (name, email, phone number)</p>
<p>   2. Booking information (dates,room preferences, requirements)</p>
<p>   3. Payment information (processed securely through our payment patners)</p>
<p>  4. Communication history related to your bookings</p>


<h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
<p>Your information is used soley for:</p>
<p>1. Processing and managing your room bookings</p>
<p>2. Communicating about your reservation and services</p>
<p>3. Sending special offers and updates (with your consent)</p>
<p>4. Improving our services and customer experience</p>
